  "meta_title": "Event Spaces in the Hamptons | Topping Rose House",
  "meta_description": "The private Hamptons event venues at Topping Rose House provide space for private dinners, social gatherings, ceremonies and meetings. Learn more.",
  "url_friendly_name": "event-spaces",
  "short_description": "<p>Picture your event in one of Topping Rose House&rsquo;s event spaces, from the rustic d&eacute;cor of the Barn to Jean-Georges Restaurant to a poolside soir&eacute;e.</p>",
  "description": "<p>From our picturesque Barn to spacious Studio, the private Hamptons event venues at Topping Rose House provide an ideal setting for a range of functions, from private dinners to poolside events, social gatherings, ceremonies and professional meetings. Each of our spaces is enhanced by seasonal menus with locally-sourced ingredients, creative seasonal cocktails and the latest audiovisual technology.</p>\n<p>From an executive team breakfast to a seated rehearsal dinner, our event venues and packages are perfect for any occasion. Our team will work with you to develop a customized experience that is sure to be memorable for all.</p>\n<p><strong>THE BARN</strong><br />Adjacent to the House, the Barn is a carefully restored vestige of the original property. Accommodating up to 60 guests for a seated lunch or dinner, and up to 100 guests for a cocktail reception with passed hors d&rsquo;oeuvres, the Barn&rsquo;s rustic d&eacute;cor provides an enchanting space for entertaining.</p>\n<p><strong>THE STUDIO</strong><br />Our largest venue at Topping Rose House, the Studio can accommodate up to 60 for a board-room style meeting, 100 for a seated meal, and 150 for a cocktail reception. Overlooking the pool and Topping Rose Orchard, the Studio uniquely combines idyllic scenery with a state of the art facility. Equipped with cutting-edge technology, it is also a perfect venue for meetings and corporate events. Floor to ceiling windows allow for ample natural light to warm a round-table discussion while black-out shades can be drawn to darken the room for a projected presentation at any time of day.</p>\n<p><strong>THE RESTAURANT</strong><br />The Restaurant at Topping Rose House may be bought out for a special celebration. Guests will experience the unique setting of their own private restaurant while mingling over cocktails and hors d&rsquo;oeuvres in the Bar Room before sitting down to a meal in our elegant and comfortable Dining Room.</p>\n<p><strong>THE ROOFDECK</strong><br />Available exclusively to guests reserved in Cottage One-Bedroom Suites, a Cottage Roofdeck offers a stunning location for a small, private celebration or gathering. Surrounded by the Hamptons' crisp fresh air and beautiful panoramic views of the property and surrounding Bridgehampton, any Roofdeck event is sure to be a memorable one.</p>",
